<div class='otherEdition' id='edition_350540'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/350540.The_Road"><img alt="The Road" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1600667691i/350540._UY200_.jpg" />
